ars, down from 1.2395 On the Commodity Exchange in <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>, gold bullion fell to $ 449.00 a troy ounce from $ 453.40 late Tuesday. In <LOCATION> London </LOCATION>, gold dropped to a late bid price of $ 449.50 a troy ounce from $ 451.50 late Tuesday. In <LOCATION> Zurich </LOCATION>, it also fell to a late bid of $ 449.50 an ounce, down from $ 453.50 bid late Tuesday. Earlier, in <LOCATION> Hong </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Kong </LOCATION>, gold dropped $ 5.60 an ounce to close at a bid $ 453.21 an ounce, down from $ 458.81 an ounce bid at Tuesday's close Silver bullion fell to a late bid of $ 6.57 a troy ounce from $ 6.65 an ounce bid late Tuesday. On <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>'s Comex, silver bullion for current delivery fell to $ 6.434 a troy ounce from $ 6.65 late Tuesday.
